<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="创业啥活都得干，做公众号，卖盒饭，顺手还混个茶叶协会。。" class="zu-question-my-bio">创业啥活都得干，做公众号，卖盒饭，顺手…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="32">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-yue-rong-19" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-yue-rong-19" class="zg-link" title="李月荣">李月荣</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yue-hua-xue-chan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yue-hua-xue-chan" class="zg-link" title="月华雪蝉">月华雪蝉</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gapsong-32" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gapsong-32" class="zg-link" title="Gapsong">Gapsong</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="6019987" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">太懒，自从在一个老板手里买了手机，之后都是在他手里买。<br>太懒，自从用了一个号码和资费，之后就一直用。<br>太懒。。。<br>一切的原因就是太懒。


</div>

